description: You will need bluplayer (http://bluplayer.net) to be launched on your PC to be able control you Bluesound HiFi system with your voice. You can start/stop player, skip songs, etc.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask blue player to skip this song
Alexa, ask blue player to play
Alexa, ask blue player to stop
name: Bluplayer
shortDescription: The skill allows you control your Bluesound HiFi system with your voice.
